# Objective

Perform regression testing after the release of a new application version. Verify that recently implemented changes have not introduced defects into previously working features.

---

# Scenario

Application Version **2.3.0** introduces the following updates:

- Improved login performance
- Added Remember Me functionality
- Updated dashboard UI
- Fixed notification loading bug

Regression testing is required to ensure existing features continue working correctly.

---

# Evaluation Criteria

| Criteria | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| Coverage | Are existing features adequately tested? |
| Accuracy | Are expected and actual results documented correctly? |
| Organization | Is the regression report easy to follow? |
| Risk Assessment | Are critical features prioritized? |
| Documentation | Are testing outcomes clearly summarized? |

