# Reflection

## What I Learned

Regression testing is essential whenever software changes are introduced. Even small updates can unintentionally affect existing functionality, making systematic regression testing a key part of maintaining software quality.

---

## What I'd Do Differently

In a production environment, I would automate repetitive regression tests using tools such as Selenium, Playwright, or Cypress. Automated regression testing reduces manual effort, improves consistency, and supports faster release cycles within CI/CD pipelines.

